<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1868-07-26T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1868-07-26T00:00:00-05:00" n="435" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d435">
                            <head><persName type="from">Mr. Washburn</persName> to <persName type="to">Señor Benitez</persName>.</head>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right">
                                    <placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United
                                            States,</hi>
                                        <hi rend="italic">Asuncion,</hi></placeName>
                                    <date calendar="gregorian" when="1868-07-26"><hi rend="italic">July</hi> 26, 1868.</date></dateline></opener>
                            <p><hi rend="smallcaps">Sir:</hi> I have just received the inclosed
                                communication from Mr. P. C. Bliss, which, at his request, I forward
                                to your honor. It treats of a matter that occurred before my return
                                to Paraguay, and of which I never heard till the day before
                                yesterday, when he told me he would write this statement. Whether it
                                will be of any use to the government I am unable to say. Hoping,
                                however, that it may be, I comply with Mr. Bliss’s request, and
                                forward it immediately.</p>
                            <p>I avail myself of this occasion to renew assurances of distinguished
                                consideration.</p>
                            <closer>
                                <signed>CHARLES A. WASHBURN.</signed></closer>
                            <postscript>
                                <p>Hon. <hi rend="smallcaps">Gumesindo Benitez,</hi>
                                    <hi rend="italic">Acting Minister of Foreign Affairs.</hi></p>
                            </postscript>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>